where do i even start this is my go to place for breakfast in charlotte i ve even came here for lunch when i worked in south park it s the bomb my favorite is the egg combo with turkey bacon and buckwheat pancakes don t forget the strawberry or apple syrup depends on what mood i m in we keep saying we re going to try the apple pancake but it s so huge i m scared lol GOODREVIEW go here it s my favorite and will be yours too it s one of those places where you become a regular and don t need a menu to order after a few trips
